ABOUT US:

Monterey Sports Cards is a father-and-son shop. My 10-year-old and I sort, scan, and list cards together in the same condition we’d want to receive ourselves. We also enjoy creating hobby-related content in our free time. Very worn cards go into bulk lots or personal stash, except for pre-1980 cards which are listed regardless of wear.


PACKAGING:

All cards ship in penny sleeves and Top Loaders or Card Savers, sealed in a Team Bag for protection. If you prefer a specific holder type, just leave a note at checkout.

Discounts apply automatically at checkout — no code needed.
